Fun AsynPortDriver for communicating with hp3458a multimeter

Series of PV's are available to the operator to take readings from the multimeter and calculate
a field strength based on the acquired measurements.

TIMER 
NUM SAMPLES 
MULTI TASK 
REPEASTS


Operator picks a num readings to take and a time value in between readings
Ok so the intended workflow is use channel access to update a PV
Updating this launches the muiltimeter TASK
The multimeter task takes samples from the multimeter and calculates an integral
These integral calculations are pushed to pv's the operator can see and use for future calibration


